{"tid":906543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★支蝗love東涌原因：「多嘢玩、買嘢平」「咖哩飯，好好味」","createTime":"2018-11-18T05:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T09:34:54.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d462adf8c75ad9f79eb1aa30fb1c23988d098242","tid":906543,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"昨日(17日)踏入大橋開通第4個周末，東涌區內雖仍有大量內地旅客聚集，但情況較早前有改善。東涌向來非旅遊熱點，《香港01》歸納四大旅客非到東涌不可的原因，當中據現場的內地旅客稱，有導遊介紹東涌區內「多嘢玩、買嘢平」，故選擇以該區為目的地。有人則慕天壇大佛之名而來。此外，由於東涌鄰近大橋，方便旅客即日來回作體驗之旅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2105708/org/71d5600fc4a950826b4f43736cd763ab.jpg/qiGyWelIm5b9JQOgA2Ck7d3Wwbj9ow8iln9EcZZ_RHE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2105708%2Forg%2F71d5600fc4a950826b4f43736cd763ab.jpg%2FqiGyWelIm5b9JQOgA2Ck7d3Wwbj9ow8iln9EcZZ_RHE&h=454f7d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首次到港的蘇小姐稱食物美味，「<span style=\"color: red;\">食咗咖哩飯，好好味</span>」，加上橋上景色優美，雖然排隊時間較長，但仍然值得，「下次會再來。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/260329/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B-%E7%95%99%E5%9C%A8%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2-%E5%B0%8E%E9%81%8A%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9%E8%B3%BC%E7%89%A9%E5%B9%B3%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9E%E5%A4%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F260329%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B-%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B6%258C%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E5%25B0%258E%25E9%2581%258A%25E4%25BB%258B%25E7%25B4%25B9%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%2599%25AF%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%25A4%259A&d=tg3Dda7iVq8UyaQIpyYsBJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=09a147b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.h